OL,5, A leading football agent who used to   
OL,6, represent Raheem Sterling has broken   
OL,7, Football Association rules by signing  
OL,8, under-age players, according to        
OL,9, evidence seen by BBC Panorama.         
OL,11,FAidy Ward also asked Mr Sterling to    
OL,12,Fspeak to a 15-year-old, as part of an  
OL,13,Fattempt by Mr Ward to sign him.        
OL,15,FMr Ward, who owns Colossal Sports      
OL,16,FManagement, said he could not comment. 
OL,18,FThe FA prohibits agents offering deals 
OL,19,Fbefore 1 January in the year of a      
OL,20,Fplayer's 16th birthday.                
